com.csipsimple.api

Class SipProfileState

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.csipsimple.api.SipProfileState
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Parcelable, Serializable

    public class SipProfileState
extends Object
implements Parcelable, Serializable
    Holder for a sip profile state.
    It allows to unpack content values from registration/activation status of a SipProfile.
    See Also:
